Declare thy scripture "A tale of enchantments in the ancient realm".

bestow the essence of wizard_name, bearing the sacred words "Merlin".  -- Conjure the essence of a mystical wizard
grant the essence of age, thusly embodying 100.  -- Manifest the essence of a mystical age
imbue the essence of is_powerful, bearing the truth.  -- Enchant the essence of a mystical power.

proclaimeth, "Greetings, fellow wizards!".  -- Unveil a sacred incantation

-- Enchanted conditions
should the essence of age be greater than 100, then
  proclaimeth, "Thou art an elder wizard, ", concatenated with the essence of wizard_name.
otherwise, should the essence of age be equal to 100, then
  proclaimeth, "Thou hast reached the pinnacle of wisdom, ", concatenated with the essence of wizard_name.
otherwise
  proclaimeth, "Thou art but a young apprentice, ", concatenated with the essence of wizard_name.

-- Loopeth through the mystical realms
forsooth, i becometh 1, and i shalt continue through 5, incrementeth by 1, do
  proclaimeth, "Casting spell number ", concatenated with i.


-- Enchanted spells
conjure the magic of invisibility, which requires nothing, thusly containing,
  proclaimeth, "I shall vanish from sight!".
Conclude.

invoke the magic of invisibility.  -- Invoke an enchanted spell

-- Tome (A mystical grimoire)
the essence of wizard_properties becometh, a collection of enchanted scrolls, thusly containing
  wand, which shall becometh the sacred words "Elder Oak",
  spellbook, that shall becometh an ancient tome containing "the wisdom of the ages",
  familiar, that shall becometh a "wise owl".

proclaimeth, "Wizard's wand: ", concatenated with the essence of the wizard_properties's wand.
proclaimeth, "Spellbook: ", concatenated with the essence of the wizard_properties's spellbook.

-- Mystical Potions (represented as enchanted vials)
the essence of potions becometh, a collection of enchanted vials, thusly containing
  "Potion of Healing",
  "Elixir of Strength",
  "Mana Draught".

-- Sip the magical elixirs
forsooth, i becometh 0 and potion becometh potions's i, do
  proclaimeth, "Sipping from the enchanted vial: ", concatenated with i, "-", concatenated with potion.